# Brewfile - Homebrew Bundle for dotfiles
# https://github.com/Homebrew/homebrew-bundle

# Taps
tap "homebrew/services"
tap "zen-browser/zen-browser"

# Command Line Tools
# =================

# Dotfile Management
brew "stow"

# Shell & Terminal
